From: Wilson

Subject: [sg-everquest] Guild Name


Greetings!

Well, The Order of Manticore is not bad. Clan Red Lions is not bad. Well, I know you people want recognition for Singapore but seriously. The guild name doesn't sound appealing hehehe!

I am on Enteri's side, on choosing Fantasy titles. They sound nicer, well at least to me, and they also fit into the game better.

And lastly, like one of you mentioned and I'm sure all of you agree. THAT THIS guild is also open to foreigners. So why make those French, Americans join "Lee Kwan Yew"? They would surely feel better with xxx<Ridgerunners> or xxx<ClintonRules> instead of xxx<SiBeiKiasu>. I believe you people get my point.

My 2 cents,

Wilson aka Yutaka
